{"id":3,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":3,"title":"Chapter 1: How We Got the Book of Mormon","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],["h1","How We Got the Book of Mormon"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p3"},"When Joseph Smith was 14 years old, many churches were claiming to be true, and he did not know which one to join."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.5-10"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:5–10"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p5"},"One day Joseph read",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/1.5"},"James 1:5"],"in the Bible: “If any of you lack wisdom, let him ask of God.” Joseph needed to know which church was right, so he decided to ask God."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.11-13"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:11–13"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p7"},"On a spring morning Joseph went into the woods near his home to pray."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.14"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p9"},"As he knelt down and started to pray, Satan tried to stop him. Joseph prayed harder, asking Heavenly Father for help."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.15-16"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:15–16"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p11"},"Heavenly Father and Jesus Christ came to Joseph in a pillar of light. Heavenly Father pointed to Jesus and said:",["span.emphasis","“This is My Beloved Son. Hear Him!”"]]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.16-17"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:16–17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p13"},"Joseph asked which church he should join. Jesus told him not to join any of them because they were all wrong."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.18-19"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:18–19"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p15"},"When Joseph told some people what he had seen and heard, they laughed at him. The leaders of many local churches persecuted him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.21-22"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:21–22"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p17"},"Three years went by. One night Joseph was praying to be forgiven of his sins and to know what he should do."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.29"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:29"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p19"},"An angel named Moroni appeared and told Joseph about a book that was written on gold plates. Joseph was to translate these plates into English."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.33-35"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:33–35"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p21"},"After Moroni left, Joseph thought about what Moroni had told him. Moroni came back two more times that night."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.44-47"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:44–47"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p23"},"The next day Joseph went to the top of the Hill Cumorah, which he had seen in a vision. There he found a big rock. He pried the rock up with a stick."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.50-52"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:50–52"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f12"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_12.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p25"},"Beneath the rock was a stone box. As Joseph looked into the box, he saw the gold plates."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.51-52"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:51–52"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f13"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_13.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p27"},"Moroni appeared and told Joseph not to take the plates but to come back on the same day each year for four years. Each time Joseph went, Moroni taught him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p28"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.53-54"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:53–54"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f14"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_14.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p29"},"After four years Joseph was finally allowed to take the gold plates. He used the Urim and Thummim to translate some of them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p30"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.59,62"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:59, 62"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f15"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_15.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p31"},"Scribes helped Joseph by writing the words as he translated them from the gold plates."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p32"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.67"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:67"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f16"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_003_16.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p33"},"Joseph took the translated words to a printer and had them made into a book."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p34"},["span.emphasis","History of the Church 1:71"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.f17"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_000_003_17.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p35"},"The book is called the Book of Mormon. It tells about people who lived in America many years ago. It also tells about Jesus Christ, the Son of God."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-1-how-we-got-the-book-of-mormon.p36"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/introduction"},"Introduction to the Book of Mormon"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
